{
  "description": "A wide-angle shot captures a dynamic scene featuring the San Francisco Bay Bridge prominently in the foreground and the iconic Golden Gate Bridge visible in the distant background. The Bay Bridge's steel structure dominates the upper portion of the image, and a portion of a dock or pier is visible on the left. Below the Bay Bridge, the water of the bay is active with a speedboat leaving a white wake as it moves across the water. The shoreline features industrial buildings and warehouses with the words \"PORT OF SAN FRANCISCO\" visible on one building. Rolling hills and distant mountains create a scenic backdrop, with the Golden Gate Bridge appearing reddish in tone against the gray hills. The sky is a light blue with wisps of clouds.",
